title: Sony XB950B1 Extra Bass Wireless Headphones with App Control, Black
feature: Feel the power of EXTRA BASS. Connectivity Technology: Wireless-Bluetooth
High quality wireless audio with Bluetooth and NFC
Optimize your sound settings with the Sony Headphones Connect app
Easily take calls wirelessly with the built-in mic
description: Bass that moves you Feel more than just the beat. EXTRABASS™ enhances all your low-end frequencies for deep power on every track. Just touch the button to get started. High-quality wireless listening Connect easily to your favorite devices via Bluetooth with NFC and enjoy high quality wirelessly streaming with built-in LDAC™ enhanced codec support. Optimize your sound settings Set the perfect sound for every Song. Sony Headphones Connect app lets you adjust your bass levels and gives you presets for club, hall, arena or outdoor style sound. Enjoy broad frequency response Large, 40 mm driver units deliver broad, dynamic and balanced sound with 20-20,000 Hz frequency response when streaming wirelessly and 3-28,000Hz with the supplied audio cable. Easily take calls wirelessly Enjoy the convenience of hands-free calling thanks to the integrated microphone and Bluetooth®1 connectivity. Simply press the phone button on the earpiece to accept incoming calls then press again to terminate the call. Music playback will automatically resume once the call is completed.
